## 🛠️ **Quick Fix Commands**

**If you get violations, use these patterns:**

```bash
# Fix inline styles
# Replace: style={{ backgroundColor: "var(--modus-wc-color-base-page)" }}
# With: class="bg-background"

# Fix colors
# Replace: style={{ color: "#000000" }}
# With: class="text-foreground"

# Fix icons
# Replace: <i class="fa fa-home"></i>
# With: <i class="modus-icons">home</i>

# Fix borders
# Replace: class="border border-red-500"
# With: class="border-destructive"
```

